data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled just a short 5-minute drive away from the picturesque Georgia International Horse Park and a mere 10-minute drive from a plethora of restaurants and retail stores, this magnificent 3-story residence is a testament to luxurious living. From the moment you step through the elegant front door, you will be captivated by the grandeur and meticulous attention to detail that defines this stunning abode.  This spacious 6-bedroom, 5-bathroom home, spanning over 4,000 square feet, is a true masterpiece of modern architecture and contemporary design. As you enter, you are greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly combines the kitchen, dining, and living areas, making it the ideal space for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, boasting a beautiful, modern design with custom cabinetry and a sleek island that is as functional as it is stylish. The main floor also features a guest suite with a full bath, providing a private oasis for your visitors. Whether you need space for guests, family, or a home office, this home provides all the flexibility you could ever need. Ascend the staircase, and you will find the epitome of luxury in the owner's retreat. This serene sanctuary offers a separate sitting room, allowing for quiet moments of relaxation or a space to read your favorite book. The spacious en-suite bathroom is a spa-like haven, complete with a jetted tub, a double vanity, and a separate shower. A substantial walk-in closet with custom cabinetry ensures that your wardrobe is well organized and easily accessible. With its prime location near the Georgia International Horse Park and a wealth of dining and shopping options Just a short drive away, this home offers the best of both worlds: a serene retreat and easy access to everything you need.  In summary, this 3-story masterpiece is more than a home; it's a lifestyle. With its breathtaking design, spacious living spaces, and thoughtful updates, this property is a testament to elegance and modern living. Welcome home to the life you've always dreamed of. Don't miss the opportunity to make this spectacular house your forever home.    A new AC unit was installed on 9/19/23. A new garage door opener on 11/02/23.
